OL,3,CHuw Edwards plaque removed from
OL,4,CCardiff Castle
OL,6,FCardiff Council has removed a plaque
OL,7,Fhonouring Huw Edwards at Cardiff
OL,8,FCastle after he admitted to having
OL,9,Findecent images of children.
OL,11,FThe former BBC presenter pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt on Wednesday to three counts of
OL,14,Fmaking indecent images of children.
OL,16,FVisitors to Cardiff Castle will no
OL,17,Flonger have access to an audio guide
OL,18,Fnarrated by the disgraced presenter,
OL,19,For see a plaque in his honour
OL,20,Fpreviously installed there.
