OL,6,FA Cardiff Council spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"The plaque on the Cardiff Castle
OL,8,FInterpretation Centre has been removed
OL,9,Fand the audio guide discontinued.
OL,10,FCardiff Council is looking at options
OL,11,Ffor a replacement narration."
OL,13,FIt comes as a mural of Edwards in his
OL,14,Fhome village has been painted over.
OL,16,FThe artwork was part of a bigger mural
OL,17,Funveiled in the presenter's home
OL,18,Fvillage of Llangennech,
OL,19,FCarmarthenshire, in 2023.
