OL,3,CHuw Edwards plaque removed from
OL,4,CCardiff Castle
OL,6,FArtist Steve Jenkins is said to have
OL,7,Fpainted over the portrait on Tuesday
OL,8,Fafter it was announced Edwards had
OL,9,Fbeen charged with three counts of
OL,10,Fmaking indecent images of children.
OL,12,FEdwards later admitted having 41
OL,13,Findecent images of children, with
OL,14,Fseven being of the most serious type,
OL,15,Fsent to him by a convicted paedophile.
OL,17,F"It's such a shame to have to do it
OL,18,Fbut charges like that are
OL,19,Fdisgraceful," Mr Jenkins, from
OL,20,FLlanelli, told the BBC after painting
OL,21,Fover the artwork.
