OL,6,F"I feel deeply saddened to have to
OL,7,Fremove it as the whole village loved
OL,8,Fit when it was first done.
OL,10,F"I was given the topic of the village
OL,11,Fto base the mural on and we thought it
OL,12,Fwould be nice if Huw was included."
OL,14,FThe artwork featured alongside many
OL,15,Feye-catching murals designed by the
OL,16,Flocal artist to freshen up an
OL,17,Funderpass, which Edwards had visited
OL,18,Fafter it was completed.
